<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN241-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṇai uṟaiyūr ēṇiccēri muṭamōciyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <rdg wit="#C2 #C3">avaṉaiya<space quantity="5" unit="character"/></rdg>
       </app>
        rēṇiccēri muṭamōciyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN241">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>tiṇtē riravalark kītta taṇṭā</l>
<l>raṇṭiraṉ varūu meṉṉa voṇṭoṭi</l>
<l>vaccirat taṭakkai neṭiyōṉ kōyiluṭ</l>
<l>pōrppuṟu muracaṅ kaṟaṅka</l>
<l>vārppeḻun taṉṟāl vicum piṉāṉē.</l></lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“Antiraṉ with a cool garland, who gave firm chariots </l>
<l corresp="1-2c">to mendicants, is coming”, so, </l>
<l corresp="4">while covered drums sounded </l>
<l corresp="2d-3">in the temple of the Tall one (~ Indra) with the vajra in [his] broad hands with bright bracelets, </l>
<l corresp="5">rose the roaring to heaven. </l>
            </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
